Package: kanotix-vdr
Architecture: all
Depends: kanotix-vdr-server, kanotix-vdr-client
Description: metapackage to install kanotix-vdr-server and -client
 This metapackage depends on kanotix-vdr-server and kanotix-vdr-client.
 It may be safely removed from your system.

Package: kanotix-vdr-server
Architecture: all
Depends: kanotix-vdr-server-data, vdr, vdr-plugin-xineliboutput, vdr-plugin-channelscan | vdr-plugin-reelchannelscan, vdr-plugin-femon, vdr-plugin-osdteletext, vdr-plugin-tvonscreen, vdr-plugin-nordlichtsepg, vdr-plugin-epgsearch, vdr-plugin-text2skin, vdradmin-am
Suggests: kanotix-vdr-server-extra
Conflicts: kanotix-vdr (<= 1.2.1-7.1), kanotix-vdr-xine (<= 1.2.1-7.1)
Description: metapackage to install the kanotix-vdr-menu and xine
 This metapackage installs kanotix-vdr-data (or kanotix-vdr-client-data) and 
 libxine-xvdr.
 It may be safely removed from your system.

Package: kanotix-vdr-server-extra
Architecture: all
Depends: kanotix-vdr-server, vdr-plugin-streamdev-server, vdr-addon-noad, vdr-plugin-newsticker, vdr-plugin-autotimeredit, vdr-plugin-premiereepg, vdr-plugin-pvrinput, vdr-plugin-radio, vdr-plugin-reelchannelscan, vdr-skins, vdr-plugin-undelete
Conflicts: kanotix-vdr (<= 1.2.1-7.1), kanotix-vdr-xine (<= 1.2.1-7.1)
Description: metapackage to install the kanotix-vdr-menu and xine
 This metapackage installs useful optional plugins for kanotix-vdr-server.
 It may be safely removed from your system.

Package: kanotix-vdr-client
Architecture: all
Depends: kanotix-vdr-client-data|kanotix-vdr-data, libxine-xvdr, libxine1, xine-ui | libxineliboutput-sxfe | xineliboutput-sxfe | libxineliboutput-fbfe | xineliboutput-fbfe | kaffeine
Replaces: kanotix-vdr-xine
Conflicts: kanotix-vdr-xine, kanotix-vdr (<= 1.2.1-7.1)
Description: metapackage to install the kanotix-vdr-menu and xine
 This metapackage installs kanotix-vdr-data (or kanotix-vdr-client-data) and 
 libxine-xvdr.
 It may be safely removed from your system.

Package: kanotix-vdr-server-data
Architecture: all
Depends: vdr, dialog, xdialog, rxvt, kanotix-su, w-pvrscan
Recommends: distro-defaults, kanotix-scripts, w-scan
Replaces: kanotix-vdr (<= 1.2.1-7.1)
Conflicts: kanotix-vdr-client-data, kanotix-vdr (<= 1.2.1-7.1), kanotix-vdr-xine (<= 1.2.1-7.1)
Provides: kanotix-vdr-data
Description: channellists, scripts and data for kanotix-vdr-server
 Ask peter_weber69 for a longer description.

Package: kanotix-vdr-client-data
Architecture: all
Depends: dialog, xdialog, rxvt, kanotix-su
Conflicts: kanotix-vdr (<= 1.2.1-7.1), kanotix-vdr-xine (<= 1.2.1-7.1)
Description: vdr-start-menu and its scripts for kanotix-vdr-client
 Ask peter_weber69 for a longer description.

Package: kanotix-vdr-xine
Architecture: all
Depends: kanotix-vdr-client
Description: metapackage to install kanotix-vdr-client
 This is a metapackage provided for compatibility reasons
 and it should only install kanotix-vdr-client, which replaces
 kanotix-vdr-xine.
